[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1358},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F05\u002F17\u002Fcomplete-express-imgur-upload-tutorial\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F05\u002F17\u002Fcomplete-express-imgur-upload-tutorial\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F05\u002F17\u002Fcomplete-express-imgur-upload-tutorial\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F05\u002F17\u002Fcomplete-express-imgur-upload-tutorial\u002F":1334,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F05\u002F17\u002Fcomplete-express-imgur-upload-tutorial\u002F":1343},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220517\u002F432259079\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1318,"date":1319,"description":19,"extension":1320,"lang":1321,"meta":1322,"navigation":799,"path":1323,"readingMinutes":1324,"seo":1325,"standalone":1326,"stem":1327,"tags":1328,"tldr":1331,"updated":1331,"url":1332,"__hash__":1333},"content\u002Fen\u002FNodejs\u002Fcomplete-express-imgur-upload-tutorial.md","The Complete Express + Imgur Upload Tutorial","4322590791",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1302},"minimark",[11,16,20,28,32,37,40,43,46,53,56,62,65,71,74,79,82,88,92,95,101,104,110,113,118,121,127,131,143,151,154,160,163,191,198,204,215,221,233,239,243,251,258,275,278,284,287,293,296,305,308,314,318,321,336,339,343,352,355,359,362,538,545,548,554,557,568,752,756,759,768,771,987,990,993,997,1000,1009,1012,1019,1028,1031,1238,1241,1244,1250,1254,1261,1268,1271,1298],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"intro","Intro",[17,18,19],"p",{},"Imgur is a really handy online photo album service with free image hosting. It's great for upload practice during dev, or even as your blog's image library. So here's a tutorial on Imgur image upload with Express.",[21,22,25],"callout",{"title":23,"type":24},"Note","note",[17,26,27],{},"This series is about Imgur, but after May 16, 2025, Imgur has blocked Taiwanese IPs from uploading images. If you're in Taiwan, consider using another image upload service.",[12,29,31],{"id":30},"imgur-prerequisites","Imgur prerequisites",[33,34,36],"h3",{"id":35},"create-an-imgur-album","Create an Imgur Album",[17,38,39],{},"First, learn how to create an Album — later, all uploaded images will be sorted into a specific Album.",[17,41,42],{},"Imgur used to let you create Albums directly, but they later hid the button and made it pretty hard to find. 80%+ of people can't find it, so follow these steps exactly.",[17,44,45],{},"Log in to Imgur. After login, click \"images\" in the user menu.",[17,47,48],{},[49,50],"img",{"alt":51,"src":52},"images","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202205172151.png",[17,54,55],{},"Find the \"All images\" dropdown — there's a \"New Album\". Click it.",[17,57,58],{},[49,59],{"alt":60,"src":61},"New Album","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202205172202.png",[17,63,64],{},"A modal pops up. Fill in the Album settings and click Save.",[17,66,67],{},[49,68],{"alt":69,"src":70},"Album","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202205172203.png",[17,72,73],{},"After creating, you'll see an empty page because we haven't added any images.",[17,75,76],{},[49,77],{"alt":69,"src":78},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-05-17%2022.04.30.png",[17,80,81],{},"Album created.",[17,83,84],{},[85,86,87],"del",{},"Great Imgur UX.",[33,89,91],{"id":90},"get-the-album-id","Get the Album ID",[17,93,94],{},"We need the Album ID later to upload images. Click \"gallery profile\" in the user menu.",[17,96,97],{},[49,98],{"alt":99,"src":100},"gallery profile","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_08.png",[17,102,103],{},"Find \"Albums\" on the right.",[17,105,106],{},[49,107],{"alt":108,"src":109},"Albums","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_10.png",[17,111,112],{},"Click \"Posts\" → \"All\". The first one is the Album you just created.",[17,114,115],{},[49,116],{"alt":69,"src":117},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_11.png",[17,119,120],{},"Open the Album and check the URL — only the part in the red box is the Album ID. Remember it, we'll use it in Express.",[17,122,123],{},[49,124],{"alt":125,"src":126},"Album ID","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_13.png",[33,128,130],{"id":129},"register-an-imgur-application","Register an Imgur application",[17,132,133,134,138,139,142],{},"Now register an Imgur application — we need ",[135,136,137],"code",{},"client_id"," and ",[135,140,141],{},"client_secret"," for upload. Click the link below:",[17,144,145],{},[146,147,130],"a",{"href":148,"rel":149},"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.imgur.com\u002Foauth2\u002Faddclient",[150],"nofollow",[17,152,153],{},"You'll see this:",[17,155,156],{},[49,157],{"alt":158,"src":159},"Register","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-05-17%2022.18.24.png",[17,161,162],{},"Required fields:",[164,165,166,175,183],"ul",{},[167,168,169,170],"li",{},"Application name\n",[164,171,172],{},[167,173,174],{},"Any name",[167,176,177,178],{},"Authorization type\n",[164,179,180],{},[167,181,182],{},"Choose \"OAuth 2 authorization without a callback URL\"",[167,184,185,186],{},"Email\n",[164,187,188],{},[167,189,190],{},"Contact info",[17,192,193,194,197],{},"PS: If you pick \"Anonymous usage without user authorization\", the \"Authorization callback URL\" needs to be ",[135,195,196],{},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com",".",[17,199,200],{},[49,201],{"alt":202,"src":203},"Application form","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_22.png",[17,205,206,207,138,209,211,212,214],{},"After applying, you'll see this. Save your ",[135,208,137],{},[135,210,141],{}," — especially ",[135,213,141],{},", don't lose it (if you do, you have to regenerate it).",[17,216,217],{},[49,218],{"alt":219,"src":220},"Application success","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_23.png",[17,222,223,224,226,227,232],{},"Application done. If you lose ",[135,225,141],{},", you can go to ",[146,228,231],{"href":229,"rel":230},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com\u002Faccount\u002Fsettings\u002Fapps",[150],"Applications"," and click \"generate new secret\".",[17,234,235],{},[49,236],{"alt":237,"src":238},"Regenerate client_secret","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_26.png",[33,240,242],{"id":241},"get-an-imgur-refresh-token","Get an Imgur Refresh Token",[17,244,245,246,138,248,250],{},"We have ",[135,247,137],{},[135,249,141],{},". The last key piece is the Refresh Token. Imgur's Token has a time limit — to auto-refresh, you need a Refresh Token.",[17,252,253,254,257],{},"Getting it is unusual — replace ",[135,255,256],{},"${Client ID}"," in this URL with the one you just got:",[259,260,265],"pre",{"className":261,"code":262,"language":263,"meta":264,"style":264},"language-html shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","https:\u002F\u002Fapi.imgur.com\u002Foauth2\u002Fauthorize?client_id=${Client ID}&response_type=token\n","html","",[135,266,267],{"__ignoreMap":264},[268,269,272],"span",{"class":270,"line":271},"line",1,[268,273,262],{"class":274},"s8XSl",[17,276,277],{},"Paste it into your browser address bar and hit Enter.",[17,279,280],{},[49,281],{"alt":282,"src":283},"Address bar","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_30.png",[17,285,286],{},"You'll hit a warning screen. As long as you confirm this is the app you want, click Allow.",[17,288,289],{},[49,290],{"alt":291,"src":292},"Allow","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_31.png",[17,294,295],{},"After allowing, you'll be redirected to Imgur. Copy the current URL — it'll look like:",[259,297,299],{"className":261,"code":298,"language":263,"meta":264,"style":264},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com\u002F#access_token=xxxxx&expires_in=xxxxx&token_type=bearer&refresh_token=xxxxx&account_username=xxxx&account_id=xxxx\n",[135,300,301],{"__ignoreMap":264},[268,302,303],{"class":270,"line":271},[268,304,298],{"class":274},[17,306,307],{},"We only need the Refresh Token. Save it.",[17,309,310],{},[49,311],{"alt":312,"src":313},"Refresh Token","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_32.png",[12,315,317],{"id":316},"imgur-final-check","Imgur final check",[17,319,320],{},"If you've followed along, you should have:",[164,322,323,326,328,331,334],{},[167,324,325],{},"An empty Album",[167,327,125],{},[167,329,330],{},"Client ID",[167,332,333],{},"Client Secret",[167,335,312],{},[17,337,338],{},"All five are required. If anything's missing, go back through the steps.",[12,340,342],{"id":341},"express-imgur","Express Imgur",[17,344,345,346,351],{},"Imgur officially provides APIs, but if there's a ready-made package, that's usually faster. We'll use the ",[146,347,350],{"href":348,"rel":349},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.npmjs.com\u002Fpackage\u002Fimgur",[150],"Imgur"," package. I'll show two versions.",[17,353,354],{},"The Imgur package has 1.x and 2.x styles, but most online examples use 1.x.",[33,356,358],{"id":357},"frontend-sample-code","Frontend sample code",[17,360,361],{},"Frontend code below — HTML is not included.",[259,363,367],{"className":364,"code":365,"language":366,"meta":264,"style":264},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","const formData = new FormData();\n  formData.append('file-to-upload', e.target.form[0].files[0]);\n  axios.post('\u002Fapi\u002Fv1\u002Fupload', formData, {\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'multipart\u002Fform-data',\n    },\n  })\n  .then((data) => {\n    console.log(data)\n  })\n  .catch(error => console.log(error));\n","js",[135,368,369,392,422,439,445,460,466,472,497,509,514],{"__ignoreMap":264},[268,370,371,375,379,382,385,389],{"class":270,"line":271},[268,372,374],{"class":373},"sOudu","const",[268,376,378],{"class":377},"stw71"," formData",[268,380,381],{"class":373}," =",[268,383,384],{"class":373}," new",[268,386,388],{"class":387},"scAaK"," FormData",[268,390,391],{"class":274},"();\n",[268,393,395,398,401,404,408,411,414,417,419],{"class":270,"line":394},2,[268,396,397],{"class":274},"  formData.",[268,399,400],{"class":387},"append",[268,402,403],{"class":274},"(",[268,405,407],{"class":406},"sWayO","'file-to-upload'",[268,409,410],{"class":274},", e.target.form[",[268,412,413],{"class":377},"0",[268,415,416],{"class":274},"].files[",[268,418,413],{"class":377},[268,420,421],{"class":274},"]);\n",[268,423,425,428,431,433,436],{"class":270,"line":424},3,[268,426,427],{"class":274},"  axios.",[268,429,430],{"class":387},"post",[268,432,403],{"class":274},[268,434,435],{"class":406},"'\u002Fapi\u002Fv1\u002Fupload'",[268,437,438],{"class":274},", formData, {\n",[268,440,442],{"class":270,"line":441},4,[268,443,444],{"class":274},"    headers: {\n",[268,446,448,451,454,457],{"class":270,"line":447},5,[268,449,450],{"class":406},"      'Content-Type'",[268,452,453],{"class":274},": ",[268,455,456],{"class":406},"'multipart\u002Fform-data'",[268,458,459],{"class":274},",\n",[268,461,463],{"class":270,"line":462},6,[268,464,465],{"cla